section.section:
This section does not:
abrogate or limit any rights of any reinsurer to claim that the reinsurer is entitled to rescind a reinsurance contract;
give a policyholder or beneficiary an independent cause of action against a reinsurer that is not otherwise set forth in the reinsurance contract;
limit or affect the Corporation's rights as a creditor of the estate against the assets of the estate; or
apply to reinsurance agreements covering property or casualty risks.
